=== VOID_WINDOW ===
# id: 10
# title: The Void Window
# chinese_title: 虚空之窗
# category: Discovery
# mode: dungeon

An observation deck offers a panoramic view of the nebula outside. The swirling gases form shapes that almost look intentional — spirals and geometric patterns painted in cosmic dust. Your mind quiets as you watch the slow celestial dance.

* [Meditate on the cosmic patterns]
  ~ gain_radical("心")
  "心" (xīn) — heart, mind
* [Chart the nebula formations]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "空" (kōng) — empty, void, sky
* [Photograph it for trade at the next port]
  ~ gain_gold(15)
  "美" (měi) — beautiful
